data.title: 1931-2011 Year Wise Telugu Complete Movies List
data.meta_description: 1931-2011 Year Wise Telugu Complete Movies List - Free ebook download as Excel Spreadsheet (.xls), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. The document lists Telugu films from 1931 to 1938. It includes the titles of over 180 films produced during this period. Some notable films included 1931's Baktha Prahalada and 1934's Paduka Pattabhishekam. The document also lists several mythological and religious films adapted from Hindu scriptures that were produced in the late 1930s. Kamalabai Gokhale was noted as one of the first Indian actresses.
